
# 🚁 Skybyte Drones – Product Line

Skybyte Drones delivers advanced UAV solutions designed for commercial, industrial, and public safety applications.


## Skybyte Falcon X
Industrial inspection drone built for infrastructure and utility monitoring.
- 4K optical zoom camera
- Thermal imaging capability
- 45-minute flight time
- AI-assisted flight stabilization


## Skybyte AgroMap Pro
Precision agriculture drone for crop analysis and smart farming.
- Multispectral sensors
- Automated field mapping
- Real-time crop health data
- Smart spraying compatibility


## Skybyte Surveyor 360
High-accuracy mapping and surveying drone for construction and land development.
- RTK/PPK positioning
- 3D terrain modeling
- Orthomosaic map generation
- Centimeter-level precision


## Skybyte AeroLite
Compact commercial drone for media and creative professionals.
- 6K video recording
- Intelligent subject tracking
- Foldable lightweight design
- Fast deployment system


## Skybyte Sentinel
Emergency response and public safety drone platform.
- Thermal and low-light cameras
- Spotlight and loudspeaker modules
- Encrypted live streaming
- Rapid response deployment kit

